Condition : 41 - Maximum noise levels within the dwellings hereby permitted shall not exceed: 
Living Rooms = 35 dB LAeq, 16hour; 
Dining room/area = 40 dB LAeq, 16hour; 
Bedrooms = 35 dB LAeq, 16 hours during day-time (07.00 ï¿½ 23.00) and 30 dB LAeq, 8hour in the night time (23.00 ï¿½ 07.00). 

The maximum noise levels described must be achieved during background ventilation rates, as defined in Part F of the Building Regulations. 

Reason: To ensure appropriate living conditions for residents in accordance with Local Plan policy EQ5 and London Plan policy D14.
